message.entry: Argument must be output data type specified as ''default'', ''double'', or ''native'', missing value condition specified as ''omitnan'', ''includenan'', ''omitmissing'', or ''includemissing'', or ''Weights'' parameter.
Dimension argument must be a positive integer scalar, a vector of unique positive integers, or ''all''.
Output data type ''native'' is not supported when weighting scheme is specified.
